msgstr ""

#: ../../../api/abc.rst:37
msgid ""
"`!dump()` can also return `!None`, to represent a :sql:`NULL` in the "
"database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.14/site-packages/psycopg/abc.py:docstring
#: of psycopg.abc.Dumper.quote:1
